   "source": [
    "# Bolzano-Weierstrass Theorem\n",
    "\n",
    "Every bounded [sequence](sequence.ipynb) has a convergent [subsequence](subsequences.ipynb). In particular, if $\\{x_n\\}$ is a sequence in $[a,b]$, then $\\{x_n\\}$\n",
    "has a subsequence $\\{x_{p_n}\\}$ that converges to a number in $[a,b]$."
   ]
  }
